
I. Dependencies

Ruby 1.9.3
Redis 2.6.x  (stable)

It is suggested to use RVM to install Ruby

II.  To install and run, execute

gem build cloud_crawler.gemspec
gem install cloud_crawler-0.1.gem 

this should install the cloud_crawler.rb  CLI  in 

/Users/charlesmartin14/.rvm/gems/ruby-1.9.3-p385/bin/cloud_crawler.rb


III.  Start redis locally

redis-server &

IV.  try a crawl

cloud_crawler.rb url-list  http://www.livestrong.com  > urls.out &


